pan></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Get script name\n\nReturns `none` if the script code is unassigned.\n\nUnicode property: `Script`\n","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getScriptName?","kind":"def","line":72,"name":"Unicode.getScriptName?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/3b873385fdbca8b43ee1e3310bf282743091a14d/UnicodeBasic.lean#L72-L80"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getScript\"><span class=\"name\">Unicode</span>.<span class=\"name\">getScript</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">char</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./UnicodeBasic/Types.html#Unicode.Script\">Script</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Get character script\n\nUnicode property: `Script`\n","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getScript","kind":"def","line":65,"name":"Unicode.getScript","sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/3b873385fdbca8b43ee1e3310bf282743091a14d/UnicodeBasic.lean#L65-L70"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getName\"><span class=\"name\">Unicode</span>.<span class=\"name\">getName</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">char</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Get character name\n\nWhen the Unicode property `Name` is empty, a unique code label is returned\nas recommended in Unicode Standard, section 4.8. These labels start with\n`'<'` (U+003C) and end with `'>'` (U+003E) so they are distinguishable from\nactual name values.\n\nUnicode property: `Name`\n","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getName","kind":"def","line":49,"name":"Unicode.getName","sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/3b873385fdbca8b43ee1e3310bf282743091a14d/UnicodeBasic.lean#L49-L59"}}],"imports":["Init","UnicodeBasic.TableLookup","UnicodeBasic.Types"],"instances":[{"className":"Membership","name":"Unicode.instMembershipCharGC","typeNames":["Char","Unicode.GC"]},{"className":"Decidable","name":"Unicode.instDecidableMemCharGC","typeNames":["Membership.mem"]}],"name":"UnicodeBasic"}